data.description: Gorgeous condo in the heart of Wintergate at Longmead Crossing.  2 bedrooms, 2 full baths with paint, flooring, lighting, blinds all updated withing the last 2 years.   Very open floorplan and lots of natural light. Plenty of parking, access to two pools, parks and recreational facilities per the condo association. In the middle of the county-Minutes to the ICC via Layhill Rd or Georgia Ave, 15 minutes to I-95 or 270.
